; preludes: form-stdlib/provisioning.fk
;
; provisioning-band — consent-to-join made falsifiable: admit iff a shared wire AND the human's yes.
;
; The field:
;   phone — join-request from "phone", offers (wifi ble). We speak (wifi audio): wifi is the shared
;           wire. The human's allowlist holds (phone): the door is open. Both consents hold -> admit.
;   ghost — join-request from "ghost", offers (zigbee) only. We speak none of that: NO shared wire.
;           The human DID open the door to it (allowlist (ghost)), but capability without a usable
;           transport is an invitation to a body we cannot reach -> NOT admitted.
;   phone against an allowlist that does NOT name it ((watch)) — a real shared wire, but the human
;           never opened the door -> NOT admitted. (isolates: capability alone does not admit.)
;
; Verdict 127 when every claim lands:
;   1   a shared-wire AND allowlisted device IS admitted     (pv-admit? phone (wifi audio) (phone) = 1)
;   2   an un-allowlisted device is NOT admitted             (the human's-yes gate drops it -> 0)
;   4   a no-shared-channel device is NOT admitted           (the capability gate drops it -> 0)
;   8   the shared-wire spine finds the overlap              (pv-shares-channel? phone (wifi audio) = 1)
;   16  the allowlist recognizes the joiner's id             (pv-allowed? phone (phone) = 1)
;   32  membership stays honest about a wire NOT offered      (pv-offers? phone "audio" = 0; phone
;                                                              offers wifi/ble, audio is ours alone)
;   64  capability alone is not consent                       (phone shares wifi yet pv-allowed? against
;                                                              (watch) = 0 -> that is why bit 2 dropped)
(do
    (let phone (list "phone" (list "wifi" "ble")))
    (let ghost (list "ghost" (list "zigbee")))
    (let mine  (list "wifi" "audio"))
    (let c0 (if (eq (pv-admit? phone mine (list "phone")) 1) 1 0))
    (let c1 (if (eq (pv-admit? phone mine (list "watch")) 0) 2 0))
    (let c2 (if (eq (pv-admit? ghost mine (list "ghost")) 0) 4 0))
    (let c3 (if (eq (pv-shares-channel? phone mine) 1) 8 0))
    (let c4 (if (eq (pv-allowed? phone (list "phone")) 1) 16 0))
    (let c5 (if (eq (pv-offers? phone "audio") 0) 32 0))
    (let c6 (if (eq (pv-allowed? phone (list "watch")) 0) 64 0))
    (add c0 (add c1 (add c2 (add c3 (add c4 (add c5 c6)))))))
